body:
Maybe add a test for the behavior of calling `hash(tensor)`, and also probably make tensor an unhashble type:
```
>>> class UnHashableTensor(object):
...    __hash__ = None

>>> t = UnHashableTensor()
>>> hash(t)
TypeError: unhashable type: 'UnHashableTensor'

```
